Cultural Context #2: The Chinese already have a name for #2019_nCov.   #冠状病毒肺炎 | 冠状 [Guānzhuàng] =crown —> coronal; 病毒 [bìngdú]= virus (literal = “sick poison”); 肺炎[fèiyán]=pneumonia. So, Guānzhuàng bìngdú fèiyán= Coronavirus pneumonia. 👇 1/2
